global: snmp-server enable traps snmp authentication linkup linkdown coldstart warmstart
interfaces:
interface Ethernet0
nameif inside
security-level 100
ip address 10.0.0.1 255.255.255.252

interface Ethernet1
shutdown
nameif outside
security-level 0
ip address 10.0.0.5 255.255.255.252

interface Ethernet2
shutdown
no nameif
no security-level
no ip address

interface Ethernet3
shutdown
no nameif
no security-level
no ip address
access_list: access-list Acl-20250413 extended permit icmp any any
access-list Acl-20250413 extended permit tcp any any
access-list Acl-20250413 extended permit udp any any
access-list Acl-20250413 extended permit ip any any
router_bgp:
router bgp 65001
bgp log-neighbor-changes
bgp router-id 10.0.0.1
vrf:
address-family ipv4 unicast
neighbor 10.0.0.2 remote-as 65001
neighbor 10.0.0.2 activate
neighbor 10.0.0.6 remote-as 65001
neighbor 10.0.0.6 activate
no auto-summary
no synchronization
exit-address-family
router_ospf:
router ospf 100
router-id 10.0.0.1
network 10.0.0.0 255.255.255.252 area 0.0.0.0
network 10.0.0.4 255.255.255.252 area 0.0.0.0
area 0.0.0.0
log-adj-changes

vrf:
ip vrf VPN-WG
rd 2516:110100000
route-target export 2516:110100000
route-target import 2516:110100000

address-family vpnv4
neighbor 222.7.0.1 activate
neighbor 222.7.0.1 next-hop-self
neighbor 222.7.0.1 send-community both
neighbor 222.7.0.2 activate
neighbor 222.7.0.2 next-hop-self
neighbor 222.7.0.2 send-community both
no auto-summary
exit-address-family

address-family ipv4 vrf VPN-WG
redistribute connected
no auto-summary
no synchronization
exit-address-family
mpls:
mpls ldp logging neighbor-changes
mls flow ip destination
mls flow ipx destination
interfaces:
interface Loopback0
ip address 222.7.0.4 255.255.255.255
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables

interface TenGigabitEthernet3/1
description TO-C1-GSR12016
ip address 222.7.0.146 255.255.255.252
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
ip pim sparse-mode
no negotiation auto
tag-switching mtu 1508
tag-switching ip
mls qos trust dscp

interface TenGigabitEthernet3/2
description TO-C2-GSR12016
ip address 222.7.0.178 255.255.255.252
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
ip pim sparse-mode
no negotiation auto
tag-switching mtu 1508
tag-switching ip
mls qos trust dscp
router_ospf:
router ospf 100
router-id 222.7.0.4
log-adjacency-changes
auto-cost reference-bandwidth 100000
redistribute connected metric 0 metric-type 1 subnets
redistribute static metric 1 metric-type 1 subnets
network 222.7.0.4 0.0.0.0 area 0
network 222.7.0.146 0.0.0.0 area 0
network 222.7.0.178 0.0.0.0 area 0
router_bgp:
router bgp 2516
no synchronization
bgp router-id 222.7.0.4
no bgp default ipv4-unicast
bgp log-neighbor-changes
neighbor 222.7.0.1 remote-as 2516
neighbor 222.7.0.1 update-source Loopback0
neighbor 222.7.0.2 remote-as 2516
neighbor 222.7.0.2 update-source Loopback0
no auto-summary

interfaces:
interface Loopback0
no shutdown
ip address 1.1.1.5 255.255.255.255

interface GigabitEthernet0/0

no shutdown
no switchport
ip address 10.0.0.10 255.255.255.252
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables

no shutdown
no switchport

no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
ip ospf network point-to-point
router_ospf:
router ospf 100
router-id 1.1.1.5
auto-cost reference-bandwidth 100000
redistribute static metric 1 metric-type 1 subnets
network 1.1.1.5 0.0.0.0 area 0
network 10.0.0.8 0.0.0.3 area 0
network 10.0.0.40 0.0.0.3 area 0
router_bgp:
router bgp 65001
bgp router-id 1.1.1.5
bgp log-neighbor-changes
neighbor 1.1.1.1 remote-as 65001
neighbor 1.1.1.1 update-source Loopback0
neighbor 1.1.1.2 remote-as 65001
neighbor 1.1.1.2 update-source Loopback0
vrf:

neighbor 1.1.1.2 activate

interfaces:
interface login
uid 2000
class super-user
encrypted-password "$1$oW1NeMUu$N7IVMfy8GfJ02jzQzJ39h/"; ## SECRET-DATA
connection-limit 5
any emergency
any notice
authorization info
interactive-commands any

interface ge-0/0/0
description TO-MX-1
address 10.0.0.2/30

interface ge-0/0/1
description TO-MX-3
address 10.0.0.9/30

interface lo0
address 1.1.1.2/32
router_bgp:
router bgp 65001
neighbor 10.0.0.9 local-address
neighbor peer-as 65001
neighbor 10.0.0.2 local-address
neighbor peer-as 65001

global: add command tecli path /bin/tecli_start description "Threat Emulation Blade shell"
set ipv6 ospf3 area backbone on
interfaces: set interface eth1 link-speed 1000M/full
set interface eth1 state on
set interface eth1 ipv4-address 10.0.0.6 mask-length 30
set interface eth2 link-speed 1000M/full
set interface eth2 state on
set interface eth2 ipv4-address 10.0.0.10 mask-length 30
set interface lo state on
set interface lo ipv4-address 1.1.1.3 mask-length 32
router_bgp: set bgp internal protocol all on
set bgp internal interface all on
set bgp internal peer 10.0.0.5 local-address 10.0.0.6 on
set bgp internal peer 10.0.0.9 local-address 10.0.0.10 on
router_ospf: set ospf interface eth1 area backbone on
set ospf interface eth2 area backbone on
set ospf area backbone range 10.0.0.4/30 restrict on
set ospf area backbone range 10.0.0.8/30 restrict on
set ospf area backbone range 1.1.1.3/32 restrict on
